name: Emmanuel House International
who_you_serve: Moms and Moms-to-Be, their Babies (Born and Unborn) and their Families in Putnam County and neighboring Westchester and Dutchess Counties who are in crisis due to unplanned pregnancies; also Women and Teens facing difficult life issues from physical and substance abuse to health, food and housing insecurity
what_you_do: Non-profit organization providing compassionate care and support to Moms and Moms-to-Be, their Babies and Families, during times of unplanned pregnancy crisis due to substance abuse, domestic violence, human trafficking, unemployment, chronic illness Offers: Infant formula distribution, Food distribution, Clothing distribution
offering: Infant formula distribution, Food distribution, Clothing distribution, Parenting classes
